Only to now be told I’ve only been receiving permits because the supervisor and clerks who report to her have been only making exceptions for me. 
This is unethical and frustrating because I ha e nowhere else to park this work vehicle, and this puts me at risk for tow and citations if I park the car within my residential area. It’s also unfair that the clerks office oversees and policies themselves, making up rules and exceptions as they go along.
